hallenges\n     - And more ...", "short_description": "BeFootball - SuperPlayer is a frenetic soccer virtual reality experience to test your best moves and sport skills while being in a breath-taking stadium.\n\nFeatured in the DEMO version:\n - Goalkeeper Mode:  become a goalkeeper and stop as many balls as possible\n - Header Mode: become a striker and head the ball to hit the scoring panels and test your accuracy.\n"}]}, "developer_name": "Prisma VR Studio", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://befootball.world/superplayer-vr-demo-privacy-policy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "https://befootball.world/legal-notice", "publisher_name": "BeFootball", "support_website_url": "https://befootball.world/contact", "website_url": "https://befootball.world/superplayer", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "2776542286000603"}, {"id": "331529188132278"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["SPORTS"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["STANDING", "ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "352800129762191"}, "review_messages": ["", "", "", ""]}]}, "cover_square_image": {"uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031354_508035390429717_751270106908215046_n.png?stp=dst-png_s360x360&_nc_cat=103&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=gU5zYsBx1BoQ7kNvgFo0gP8&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBec4-n2L1IfqLN1NMKqjtMBZsFyJG5noYLbLGVWn_nTw&oe=67320665"}, "is_concept": false, "is_test": false, "is_trial_offer_valid": false, "display_name": "BF Super Player Demo", "platform": "ANDROID_6